com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api

Class VenuesApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.VenuesApi

  • public class VenuesApi
extends Object
    An abstract representation of Venues API endpoint. Provides executors that can be used to handle all venue-related requests.
